Production free Salesforce Org Login

Steps to sign up for a free Salesforce Developer Org:

1. Open [Salesforce Developer Signup](https://developer.salesforce.com/signup?utm_source=chatgpt.com)
2. Enter your First Name and Last Name
3. Enter your Email
4. Select Country/Region
5. Enter a Company name (you can enter your name)
6. Create a Username

   * Example: `yourname123@gmail.com`
   * ⚠️ It must be unique globally
7. Accept the terms and click Sign me up
8. Check your email
9. Click the verification link
10. Set your password
11. Log in to your free Salesforce Developer Org

Easy to remember: Signup → Email Verify → Password → Login



